<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[The very last page sort of bothered me... Could someone help me put to rest my confusion on the description of The Seagulls of Somerset? Was that Harry's book and Marcus claimed it was Luther's, keeping Harry's authorship to The Origin of Evil intact? Or was it stating things honestly and posthumously honoring Luther with The Origin of Evil? It just sat strange with me. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
