  <span id="freeText314637409122884190" style="display:none">There's few books out there that grab you from the first page and keep you there to the last page. There's even fewer books that actually make you feel like you're on a journey. It's a long book but I wish it was longer. I'm missing the characters already. This book has everything, it's a thriller, it has humour, sadness, character development, love, lies and deception. I want more!!</span>
